  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Worker Tuning \u2014 SDK Metrics",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "\nThe worker side of **Flow 2 (Workflow Progress)**. The other dashboards are server-side; these\nSDK metrics live in the worker process and are the levers for worker tuning.\n\nMetrics are **`temporal_`-prefixed** and pulled from the worker `/metrics` endpoints. The Python SDK\nexposes **counters without `_total`** (e.g. `temporal_workflow_task_queue_poll_succeed`). Latency\nhistograms are bare **`*_latency_bucket`** with values **in seconds** \u2014 sdk-core's `unit_suffix` is off\nby default, so `durations_as_seconds=True` sets the value unit, not the name (a Tally Go/Java worker\nwould instead expose `*_latency_seconds_bucket`). Complements the existing **Temporal SDK** dashboard (which\ncovers workflow/activity execution latency & throughput).\n\n> Several metric names below depend on SDK/build (`temporal_worker_task_slots_available`,\n> `temporal_sticky_cache_*`, `temporal_num_pollers`). Blank panels mean the metric isn't emitted.\n> Prometheus isn't published to the host \u2014 confirm names via Grafana's datasource proxy:\n> `POST localhost:3000/api/datasources/proxy/uid/prometheus/api/v1/query`.\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Slots & Pollers",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8
      },
      "id": 2,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Task Slots Available by Worker Type",
      "description": "Slots near 0 = worker saturated; raise max_concurrent_*_task slots. metric: temporal_worker_task_slots_available",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9
      },
      "id": 3,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "avg by (worker_type) (temporal_worker_task_slots_available)",
          "legendFormat": "{{worker_type}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Pollers by Type",
      "description": "metric: temporal_num_pollers",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 9
